Barbra: The Music… The Mem’ries… The Magic!

IMDb: 7.5

1h 48min

Iconic songstress Barbra Streisand culminates her 13-city tour in Miami with dazzling ballads, Broadway standards and stories from behind the scenes.

Genre: Documentary, Music

Rose Morgan, who still lives with her mother, is a professor of Romantic Literature who desperately longs for passion in her life. Gregory Larkin, a mathematics professor, has been burned…

The Prince of Tides
